    <category term="網路漏洞" scheme="https://brianlien09.github.io/tags/%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>路徑穿越漏洞：讀取你不該讀取的檔案</title>
    <link href="https://brianlien09.github.io/20240804/development_plan_study/path-traversal/"/>
    <id>https://brianlien09.github.io/20240804/development_plan_study/path-traversal/</id>
    <published>2024-08-04T08:23:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-09-11T15:44:23.000Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;路徑穿越 (Path Traversal)，也稱為目錄穿越 (Directory Traversal) 或「點-點-斜線 (dot-dot-slash)」攻擊，是一種允許攻擊者存取網站伺服器上任意檔案的漏洞。透過操縱檔案路徑，攻擊者可以讀取到網站根目錄之外的敏感檔案，例如設定檔、原始碼，甚至是系統層級的密碼檔案。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="安全達人養成計劃" scheme="https://brianlien09.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA%E9%A4%8A%E6%88%90%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/"/>
    
    
    <category term="網路漏洞" scheme="https://brianlien09.github.io/tags/%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>帳戶接管風險：不安全的密碼變更功能</title>
    <link href="https://brianlien09.github.io/20240804/development_plan_study/insecure-password-change-function/"/>
    <id>https://brianlien09.github.io/20240804/development_plan_study/insecure-password-change-function/</id>
    <published>2024-08-04T08:22:14.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-09-11T15:44:23.000Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;密碼變更功能是任何使用者系統的核心部分，但如果設計不當，它可能成為攻擊者接管帳戶的直接途徑。一個不安全的密碼變更功能，會讓攻擊者在未經適當授權的情況下，擅自修改受害者的密碼。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="安全達人養成計劃" scheme="https://brianlien09.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA%E9%A4%8A%E6%88%90%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83/"/>
    
    
    <category term="網路漏洞" scheme="https://brianlien09.github.io/tags/%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E/"/>
    
